{"tid":2065973,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"調查指12%僱主計劃裁員 短期就業市場受壓","createTime":"2020-06-16T03:14:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-16T07:33:45.000Z","uid":166360,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"dba52d1273dba5781a66a201a1d9ed3af85bffb1","tid":2065973,"uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T03:14:18.000Z","msg":"調查指12%僱主計劃裁員 短期就業市場受壓<br />\n2020-06-16 HKT 10:59<br />\n<br />\n一項調查顯示，約12%僱主表示，第3季有需要縮減人手，76%表示人手將會維持不變。<br />\n<br />\n人力資源機構Manpower Group在4月底，訪問了137名僱主。機構認為，疫情下香港失業率上升，僱主招聘意欲疲弱，短期內就業市場仍會受壓，亦留意到有企業在市場不確定情況下，尋求靈活招聘方案，包括臨時工或合約工招聘程序外判。<br />\n<br />\n另外，機構把預期人力需求增加的僱主百分比，減去預期人力需求減少的僱主百分比，得出淨就業展望指數。<br />\n<br />\n以行業劃分，金融保險及房地產業的淨就業展望指數錄得負2%，按季及按年分別下跌5及22個百分點。批發零售業亦錄得負2%，按季及按年分別下跌3及19個百分點。至於服務業錄得9%，按季上升9個百分點，但按年下跌12個百分點。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1532317-20200616.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1532317-20200616.htm&d=UliE8fwpyfwMZiesMcCM7mLZ6li1RkmcNQmTobTGNbY%3D&h=2a669515\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1532317-20200616.htm&h=1d81735e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1532317-20200616.htm</a>"},{"pid":"da2f715b78baca4892a50e101fd0c5799b5ab80b","tid":2065973,"uid":198783,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T03:20:45.000Z","msg":"Manpower<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"200c6de02c667e141fd5b95cb5f12195711a8bec","tid":2065973,"uid":53062,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T03:27:50.000Z","msg":"金融保險及房地產業的淨就業展望指數錄得負2%<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6305291af1de720086b8e6963a740424496d16e","tid":2065973,"uid":237425,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T04:22:33.000Z","msg":"12%僱主裁員=12%+失業率?! <img src=\"